Tremor finally arrives to Mt. Fuji.  He notices that the 
constructicons work outside the ship had finished by itself.  (I want 
it done so...) There was now a large metal sheet that would retract 
to allow people inn and another one at the base of the mountain.He 
opens a link to Apeface.  "Apeface, Tremor here.  I have SLuggy 
and, well he is kinda dead, I think.  You wanna let us in. " Tremor 
then looks around as he hears t he faint sounds of a jet. but 
doesn't see  anything.

JetV sees the ground ahead and dives down into the water 
shooting back up quickly and transforming to his ATV mode.  He 
drives through the trees to the base of the mountain, just out of 
sight of the entrace there.
=-=-=-=-=-==-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

Dreadwing comes to a complete stop in mid air as the farage of 
bullets whiz in front of him.  The missiles had a different idea 
though as they slammed underneath him.  He went into a crazy 
dive straigh at the ship then pulled up leveling along the ship.  
Letting two missiles whiz at the missile launcher before circling a 
way.

=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

Seekker followed.  Seeing Lokk looking for some bullets he runs up 
to him pointing one of his miniguns straight at his face.  "I'vre got 
bullets, ya want some, huh, do ya?" he said in a gansta voice.
